---
layout: base.njk
title: Über uns
description: Erfahren Sie mehr über Clubshot.
lang: de
---
<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8 text-center mt-4">
            <div class="mb-4">
                <img src="/assets/Clubshotv2.1.svg" alt="Clubshot Logo" height="80" class="mb-3">
            </div>
            <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-4">{{ translations[lang].aboutTitle }}</h1>
            <p class="lead mb-4">{{ translations[lang].aboutText1 }}</p>
            <p class="fs-5 text-muted mb-5">{{ translations[lang].aboutText2 }}</p>
            
            <hr class="my-5">
            
            <h3 class="fw-bold mb-3">Kontakt</h3>
            <p class="text-muted">Interesse geweckt? Kontaktieren Sie uns für weitere Informationen.</p>
            <a href="mailto:info@myclubshot.de" class="btn btn-primary rounded-pill px-5 my-3">info@myclubshot.de</a>
            
            <div class="mt-5">
                <a href="/{{ lang }}/" class="btn btn-outline-secondary rounded-pill px-4">{{ translations[lang].home }}</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>